VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(pickle\.load\(.*\)|pickle\.loads\(.*\)|shelve\.open\(.*\))
WHEN EXPR MISSING:(trusted|signed|verify|hmac|safe_serialization)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects insecure usage of the pickle and shelve modules, which can introduce deserialization vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Serialization: pickle and shelve.
